<h2>Brew Method: French Press</h2>
<div>
    <div  class=brewimage>
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-press.png" %>
    </div>
  <p>
  	The French Press (or Press Pot, Cafetière) is a full immersion, non-filtered brew method. Some key identifiers for this method are: full bodied, heavier mouth-feel, and an oilier finish.  
  </p>
</div>





