<h3>Instructions</h3>
<div>
  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-preheat-water.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>1. Preheat water and pour into press pot and desired drinking vessel to warm.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-grind-beans.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>2. Measure beans on scale according to bean water ratio and grind beans in burr grinder. *(Remember to remove pre-heat water from vessels before adding coffee)</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-bloom-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>3. Tare press pot with beans on a scale. Pour enough water to cover all the beans, stir, and let bloom.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-immersion-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>4. Using the scale to measure, pour the remaing water ratio into the press pot and replace lid with plunger, but do not plunge.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: left">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-plunge-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 30px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsleft>5. After immersion time is finished, with control gently press down on plunger over 10-20 sec.</p>
  </div>

  <div class=instructions>
      <div style="float: right">
        <%= image_tag "coffee-experiments-decant-press.png",:width => "100px", :style=>"margin-left: 35px; margin-right: 50px"%>
    </div>

      <p class=instructionsright>6. Dispose of pre-heat water and decant brew from press pot into warmed vessel.</p>
  </div>
</div>

